{"tid":1727974,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"警員涉報案室偷拍性感女 高層震怒開file查","createTime":"2019-11-16T16:09:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-16T16:13:15.000Z","uid":132587,"like":5,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"a07e7ece3be2a33bea709b8f1b214a5a86629761","tid":1727974,"uid":132587,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:09:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.imgur.com/9ImhlLp.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.imgur.com%2F9ImhlLp.png&h=dbc558c7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n尖沙嘴警署今日發生警員涉在報案室內偷拍女報案人事件！涉事的2張相片下午開始在網上瘋傳，事件不斷發酵，引起全城怒吼。據知警方高層震怒，並高度關注事件，正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n據《蘋果》收到的相片所見，其中一張相片明顯影到，一名身穿黑色低胸背心的長髮女子站於報案室櫃檯前，正面向一名報案室警員，而該警員則坐著全神貫注在電腦上紀錄案件。從相片的角度估計，拍攝者涉嫌是警署內部人員。而另一張是趁報案女子坐下低頭睇手機時，拍攝者以手機「高炒」，正好拍攝到女子的上半身。<br />\n<br />\n據消息稱，拍攝現場為尖沙嘴警署，於今日下午拍攝，而拍攝者為一名警員，其後將相片外傳，最後被放上網而引發事件。根據指引，警員不可以在警署內拍攝，涉事警員疑違反紀律，警方正展開調查。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20170801/57030196?fbclid=IwAR0zefTWjqcLuUNc4M3w9IS7hYTfYTCXikLPPK-KWEp6uJ0B-lEXZ1FKZfE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170801%2F57030196%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0zefTWjqcLuUNc4M3w9IS7hYTfYTCXikLPPK-KWEp6uJ0B-lEXZ1FKZfE&d=VpJPAaQEVg4A3L06AjdBQEzKa5je2Ql9GrxhcbxOrro%3D&h=e2fb2a49\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20170801%2F57030196%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR0zefTWjqcLuUNc4M3w9IS7hYTfYTCXikLPPK-KWEp6uJ0B-lEXZ1FKZfE&h=eddf9fc9\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20170801/57030196?fbclid=IwAR0zefTWjqcLuUNc4M3w9IS7hYTfYTCXikLPPK-KWEp6uJ0B-lEXZ1FKZfE</a>"},{"pid":"911a7d763f268dbe5766ba16abe9b0e48dd526b0","tid":1727974,"uid":273157,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-16T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"old news is so exciting"},{"pid":"3d4a07ccf2d0613274d5e220904fe65e1108a1f9","tid":1727974,"uid":62512,"like":1,"d